星町水成将参与 Sukima Switch 首张致敬专辑《Minna no Sukima Switch》 https://p2y.jp/hoshimachi-suisei-to-participate-in-sukimaswitch-first-tribute-album/ https://p2y.jp/hoshimachi-suisei-to-participate-in-sukimaswitch-first-tribute-album/#respondp2y_admin Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:00:01 +0000 VTuberバーチャル音楽CDTwitterYouTubeYouTuberスキマスイッチバーチャルYouTuberバーチャルシンガーホロライブホロライブプロダクション星街すいせい https://p2y.jp/?p=122672 <p>据消息，VTuber Suisei Hoshimachi（所属：Hololive）将参与 Sukima Switch 定于 5 月 29 日发行的首张致敬专辑《Minna no Sukima Switch》。 “苏克[…]</p><a href="https://p2y.jp/hoshimachi-suisei-to-participate-in-sukimaswitch-first-tribute-album/">星町水成将参与 Sukima Switch 首张致敬专辑《Minna no Sukima Switch》</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>据消息，VTuber <strong>Suisei Hoshimachi</strong> （所属：Hololive）将参与 Sukima Switch 定于 5 月 29 日发行的首张致敬专辑《 <strong>Minna no Sukima Switch</strong> 》。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="122677" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/hoshimachi-suisei-to-participate-in-sukimaswitch-first-tribute-album/hoshimachi_suisei_to_participate_in_sukimaswitch_first_tribute_album/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/hoshimachi_suisei_to_participate_in_sukimaswitch_first_tribute_album.png" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="hoshimachi_suisei_to_participate_in_sukimaswitch_first_tribute_album" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/hoshimachi_suisei_to_participate_in_sukimaswitch_first_tribute_album.png" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/hoshimachi_suisei_to_participate_in_sukimaswitch_first_tribute_album.png" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/hoshimachi_suisei_to_participate_in_sukimaswitch_first_tribute_album.png" alt="" class="wp-image-122677"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">图片来源：X（推特）<br> © 奥古斯塔办公室有限公司</figcaption></figure><p></p><p>`` <strong>SUKIMASWITCH 20 周年纪念专辑《Everyone&#39;s Sukima Switch》</strong>将收录 11 名与 Sukima Switch 相关或尊重 Sukima Switch 的艺术家，每一位都将翻唱他们对 Sukima Switch 的美好回忆的歌曲。星町水成将参与《<strong>黄金时光恋人</strong>》的封面。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="SUKIMASWITCH - “GOLDEN TIME RUBBER”音乐视频：SUKIMASWITCH / GOLDEN TIME RUBBER 音乐视频" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0iAF8TJAqp4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="[星町水成] Golden Time Lover / Sukima Switch (钢之炼金术师) [歌曲框架剪切] (2021/03/08) 星町水成" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/enOyi_cDLJM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><p> 《SUKIMASWITCH 20周年纪念专辑‘大家的Sukima Switch’》预定于5月29日发行。 </p><p></p><div class="kaerebalink-box" style="text-align:left;padding-bottom:20px;font-size:small;zoom: 1;overflow: hidden;"><div class="kaerebalink-image" style="float:left;margin:0 15px 10px 0;"> <a h